Event Espresso is the leading live event and ticket management solution for WordPress. With this integration, you can associate your online courses to live events so that when users register, they are auto-enrolled. Perfect for anyone offering live training, seminars, or classrooms.

= Integration Features = 

* Easily map an event to a course
* Associate one, or many, courses
* Drip-feed course content leading up to an event
* Works with any Event Espresso payment gateway

Note: this integration requires Event Espresso v4 or higher.

See the [Add-on](https://learndash.com/add-on/event-espresso/) page for more information.

